targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  avg(ava_debt)   as 'debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and ava_debt > 0

SELECT
  avg(exp_debt)  as 'debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and exp_debt > 0

SELECT
  avg(lat_debt)  as 'debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and lat_debt > 0

SELECT 1 as 'debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE $__timeFilter(start) 
group by family
having sum(ava_debt) > 0

SELECT 1 as 'no debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE $__timeFilter(start) 
group by family
having sum(ava_debt) = 0

SELECT 1 as 'debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE $__timeFilter(start) 
group by family
having sum(exp_debt) > 0

SELECT 1 as 'no debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE $__timeFilter(start) 
group by family
having sum(exp_debt) = 0

SELECT 1 as 'debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE $__timeFilter(start) 
group by family
having sum(lat_debt) > 0

SELECT 1 as 'no debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE $__timeFilter(start) 
group by family
having sum(lat_debt) = 0

SELECT
  family, 
  avg(ava_debt) as 'debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and ava_debt > 0 
group by family

SELECT
  family, 
  avg(exp_debt) as 'debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and exp_debt > 0 
group by family

SELECT
  family, 
  avg(lat_debt) as 'debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) and lat_debt > 0 
group by family

SELECT
  Date(start) AS "time",
  family,
  avg(nullif(ava_debt, 0)) as 'availability debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) 
group by start, family

SELECT
  start AS "time",
  family,
  ifnull(avg(nullif(exp_debt, 0)), 0) as 'experience debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) 
group by start, family

SELECT
  start AS "time",
  family,
  ifnull(avg(nullif(lat_debt, 0)),0) as 'latency debt'
FROM MonthlyJourney
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(start) 
group by start, family
